PrecisEnactment of the PROPERTY ASSESSMENT AND TAXATION (RAILWAY RIGHT-OF-WAY) REGULATIONS which establish a formula for determining the assessed value of real property interests held by the Canadian Pacific Railway Company or by utility systems in right-of-way corridors located on some Indian Reserves in British Columbia, and the initial and future tax rates.
